Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us like to contemplate \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,being in a serious accident or receiving news \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.29,0:00:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have a very serious illness \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that may even be life threatening. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When the blood issue also arises, \Nat such times, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of course we’re all determined \Nthat we’re going to keep our integrity. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But we also feel the need \Nfor comfort and for support \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we can remain faithful.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Jehovah never promised \Nfor this period of time \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that we would receive miraculous healing. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But he did promise that we would receive \Nsomething very significant. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you open your Bibles with me? \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s look together at Psalm 41:3. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It says: “Jehovah will sustain him \Non his sickbed; \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:01:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,during his sickness \Nyou will completely change his bed.”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now, The Watchtower, back in 2008, \Nthe September 15 issue,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,just made a nice little comment \Non this verse. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It said: \N“David did not expect Jehovah \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,“to perform \Na miracle and remove [his] sickness. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,“Rather, David felt certain \Nthat Jehovah would ‘sustain him’\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.16,0:01:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,“—that is, give him support and strength \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,while he was lying on his sickbed.” \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that’s what Jehovah has promised. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s promised that he’s going to provide us \Nwith the support and the strength \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.31,0:01:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that we need\Nso that we can keep our integrity.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Hospital Information Services (HIS) \Nhere in Brooklyn, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the Hospital Information Desks \Nat each of the branches, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Hospital Liaison Committees (HLC) \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.89,0:01:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,have been very powerful tools \Nin the hand of Jehovah \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to provide this support and strength \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,when the blood issue arises. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know that now worldwide \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there are some 1,700\N—that is 1,700—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hospital Liaison Committees \Nwith over 13,000 members?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not easy work. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The vast majority of these brothers \Nare not physicians; \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they’re not connected \Nto the medical community in any way. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Often, they have to get up \Nin the middle of the night \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to go to the hospital. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they deal \Nwith very confrontational situations. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually all of the situations \Nthat they deal with are emotionally charged. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Their work is very seldom seen by others. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not in the spotlight.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when we reflect on the work \Nof these wonderful brothers \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,who are willing to accomplish this work \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of giving assistance and \Nsupport and help to our brothers, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:03:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we can’t help but think of this scripture \Nin Jeremiah chapter 23, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,where Jehovah says— \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeremiah 23:4: \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,“‘And I will raise up over them shepherds \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“‘who will really shepherd them. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,“‘They will no longer be afraid \Nor be terrified,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and none will be missing,’ \Ndeclares Jehovah.” \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that’s exactly \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what the Hospital Liaison Committee \Nbrothers do. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They are wonderful shepherds \Nwho are there to help the brothers \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to have the information \Nand the assistance they need \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so that they can maintain their integrity.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I recall one experience when I was working \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Hospital Information Desk in Canada. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A sister in a northern Canadian city, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,she had been very, very seriously injured. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She had to be airlifted to a larger center \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,where she would be able to receive \Nmore intensive care. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:04:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hospital Liaison Committee member \Nwas immediately notified; \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,he went to the hospital. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, as soon as the aircraft landed \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sister was being taken off \Nand wheeled into the hospital, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,there the brother was waiting in the hallway. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, when he approached her \Nlying on the stretcher, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the sister was trembling with fear. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when he looked down at her, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,she looked up and she said, \N“Are you a doctor?” \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And he said, \N“No, I’m your brother.” \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, immediately the sister\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,—this huge sigh of relief \Nbecause now there was someone \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,who could give her the practical help \Nthat she so much needed.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what are some of the ways \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that this arrangement \Ndoes provide practical support? \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I’m not sure if you know this, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but at 89 branch offices around the world\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,—including the United States and Canada—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,we have brothers who are on call \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:05:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,24 hours a day, seven days a week \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to answer calls \Nfrom Hospital Liaison Committee members \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and also from doctors \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,who request assistance \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,on how to treat Jehovah’s Witnesses \Nwithout the use of blood.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an amazing arrangement. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When I worked with HIS, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I recall many times \Nin the middle of the night, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we would receive calls \Nfrom a brother or a sister \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,or from an HLC or from a doctor \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,about someone who \Nwas desperately in need of assistance. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And the organization \Nhad provided such wonderful tools. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, \Na database has been assembled \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of literally thousands of medical articles \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,from respected medical journals. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now these articles can be sent \Nto a doctor or to a medical team, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and they explain very specifically \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,what can be done to address a situation \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,without the use of a blood transfusion. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:06:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Often, when a doctor \Nreceives an article like that\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,—he sees it’s from one of his peers, \Nit’s been published in a respected journal—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,he is much more willing to cooperate. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, he sees \Nin a practical way what can be done.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But even better, \Neach Hospital Information Desk \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,maintains a list of consulting doctors. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, these are \Nvery well-respected physicians \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,who are not afraid \Nto confer with other doctors \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and explain to them how \Neven very complex, very difficult cases \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,can be managed without the use of blood.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I recall one time in the middle of the night, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we received a call about a sister \Nwho had just given birth, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and she had lost \Na significant amount of blood. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor managing her case \Nwas very interested in receiving help. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we called \Na very, very well-respected professor \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,of obstetrics and gyneocology \Nin Canada \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,who was always willing \Nto provide assistance. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I started off the call by saying, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,“I’m so sorry to call you so late at night.” \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the doctor said: \N“Please don’t apologize, Mark. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m always happy to do anything \NI can to help the sisters.” \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course, \Nhe was not a Witness himself. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But he viewed those dear ones \Nas his own sisters, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and he was willing to help them.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, such courageous and skilled physicians \Nall around the world \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,have done so much to help our brothers. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And the tools just keep on improving. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of you may know \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that now we have a section \Nfor medical professionals \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,on our jw.org website. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I’ll reiterate: \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a site or an area \Nfor Jehovah’s people; \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s specifically designed \Nfor medical professionals. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But that area, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,although it’s only recently been established, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is already having a wonderful effect.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me relate this experience. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A sister wrote this into the branch. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She said: “Recently my husband took me \Nto the emergency room, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,“and we discovered \NI had a mass of some sort near my appendix \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,“and that a huge \Nand possibly messy surgery \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,“was needed to discover the problem. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,“When I told the surgeon \Nthat was assigned to me \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,“that I was one of Jehovah’s Witnesses, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,“he became agitated when I reinforced \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,“my nonnegotiable stand. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,“He never became rude or harsh, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,“but I could tell that he was very troubled. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,“My husband left \Nto make a phone call to the brothers. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,“Five minutes later, \Na resident came to tell me \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,“that the surgeon \Nhad just gone to the jw.org website \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,“and was downloading information. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,“We had never mentioned the website. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,“How he knew or who told him, \Nwe’ll never know. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,“But ten minutes later, \Nhe came back with copies of the information. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,“He had read it, \Nhe had marked the pages, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,“and he went over everything \Nwith my husband and me. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,“Then he took my hand, and he smiled. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,“He asked if I was ready, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,“and he promised to do his very best for me. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,“He said he too had made \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,“some nonnegotiable decisions \Nwith God in his lifetime. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“He saw me about 12 hours after the surgery, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,“and I teased him about being a trouble. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,“He said, ‘No, it was extraordinary.’ \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,“We know he meant what he had just learned \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,“about the Hospital Liaison Committee \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and Jehovah’s provision \Nfor information for His people.” \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The sister concluded by saying, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,“I have never felt \Nsuch a wave of peace from Jehovah \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in all my years in the truth.”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Jehovah did not promise us \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,miraculous healing at this time, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but he did promise \Nthat he would provide us \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with support and strength \Nwhen we are sick. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful gift Jehovah \Nhas given his people \N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,through the fine work \Nof the Hospital Liaison Committees! \N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, this has been \Na strengthening aid for us \N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,“to keep abstaining from . . . blood.”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.39,0:00:06.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,わたしたちはだれも\N重大な事故に遭ったり—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:10.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,命を脅かすような\N重い病気と診断された時のことを—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:13.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,考えたいとは思いません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:18.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,しかし そうした状況で\N血の問題が起きる場合—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:23.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,もちろん忠節を保ちたいと\N決意するでしょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:30.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,しかし 信仰にとどまれるよう\N慰めや支えも必要です\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:33.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバは今の時代—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:38.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,奇跡によって病気を回復させるとは\N保証しておられません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:43.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,しかし とても重要な あることは\N約束しておられます\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:46.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,ご一緒に聖書を開きましょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.63,0:00:50.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,詩編 41編3節です\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:52.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,こうあります—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:56.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,“エホバご自身が病の床にある\N 彼を支えてくださいます”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:58.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,“あなたは彼の病気の間—”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:01:02.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,“そのすべての寝床を\N 必ず替えてくださいます”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:03.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,この聖句に関して—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:07.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,「ものみの塔」\N 2008年9月15日号に—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:09.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,興味深いコメントがありました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:13.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,“ダビデはエホバが奇跡によって\N 病気を取り除いてくださるとは—”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:15.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,“期待していませんでした”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:18.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,“むしろ エホバが\N「自分を支えてくださる」—”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:21.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,“つまり病床にある自分を支援し—”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.36,0:01:26.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,“力を与えてくださることを\N 確信していたのです”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:30.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,これがエホバの約束です\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.07,0:01:32.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバは\Nわたしたちが忠節を保てるよう—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:36.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,支えと力を与えてくださるのです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:41.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,ブルックリンのホスピタル･\Nインフォメーション･サービス—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:45.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,各支部の医療機関情報デスク—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:50.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,各国の医療機関連絡委員会は\N血の問題が起きる時—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:53.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,このエホバのみ手による\N支えと力を与えるために—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:57.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,非常に力強い働きをしてきました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:03.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,世界にはおよそ1700の\N医療機関連絡委員会があり—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:09.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,1万3000人以上が奉仕していることを\Nご存じでしょうか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:14.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,簡単な仕事ではありません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:21.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,兄弟たちの多くは医師ではなく\N医療機関とのコネも全くありません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:26.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,兄弟たちは病院に行くために\Nよく深夜に起こされます\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:30.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,時には非常に難しい状況もあります\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:35.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,彼らが対処する状況の多くは\N緊迫したものです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:40.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,他の人から働きが見られることは\Nほとんどありません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:43.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,注目されることはないのです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:45.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,これら素晴らしい兄弟たちが—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:49.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,他の人たちに援助や支え\N助けを与えるため—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:52.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,喜んで果たす奉仕について\N思い巡らすと—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:57.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,エレミヤ 23章のエホバの言葉が\N思い浮かびます\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:01.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,エレミヤ 23章4節—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:05.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,“「そして わたしは彼らを\N 実際に牧する牧者たちを—”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:08.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,“彼らの上に起こす”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:13.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,“彼らはもはや恐れることも\N 恐怖の念を抱くこともなく—”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:19.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,“だれひとり失われないであろう」と\N エホバはお告げになる”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:25.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,医療機関連絡委員会は\Nまさにこのことを行なっています\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:29.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,彼らは必要な情報や支えを\N与えてくれる—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:32.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,素晴らしい牧者たちなのです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:36.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,それによって兄弟たちは\N忠節を保つことができるのです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:41.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,わたしがカナダの医療機関情報デスクで\N働いていた時のことを—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:43.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,お話ししましょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:48.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,北部の街で ある姉妹が\N大きな事故に遭いました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,集中治療を受けるため—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:55.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,高度医療センターに\Nヘリで搬送されました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:04:02.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,すぐに医療機関連絡委員の兄弟に\N知らされ 兄弟は病院へ行きました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:08.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,ヘリが到着し 姉妹が降ろされ\N病院に担ぎ込まれると同時に—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:12.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,兄弟も病院の玄関に到着しました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:15.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,姉妹の横たわるストレッチャーに\N近づくと—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:18.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,姉妹は恐怖で震えていました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:23.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,のぞき込むと 姉妹は兄弟を見上げ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,「お医者さんですか？」と尋ねました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,「いいえ あなたの兄弟です」\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:33.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,すると姉妹は フーッ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,必要な助けを与えてくれる兄弟がいて—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:39.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,ホッとため息をつきました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:45.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,この取り決めによって与えられる\N実際的な援助には—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,どのようなものがあるでしょうか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,ご存じかどうか分かりませんが—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:56.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,米国とカナダを含む\N世界の89の支部には—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:59.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,医療機関連絡委員会や\Nエホバの証人に—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:03.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,無輸血治療を行なうための\N援助を求める医師からの電話を—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:09.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,年中無休24時間体制で\N受ける兄弟たちがいます\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:16.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,これは驚くべき奉仕です\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:21.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,HISで奉仕していた時\N兄弟姉妹やHLC—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:28.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,切実に助けを必要としている\N医師からの電話をよく深夜に受けました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:33.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,また 組織には\N素晴らしいツールがあります\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,例えば—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:42.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,信頼できる医学雑誌から取られた\N何千もの文献のデータベースがあります\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:48.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,これらの文献は医師や\N医療チームに送られ—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:51.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,無輸血で治療を行なうには\Nどうすればよいかを—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:55.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,明確に説明するものとなっています\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:06:02.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,医師はそのような文献を受け取ると\N同僚が書いたものだったり—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:05.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,権威ある雑誌から取られていることに\N気づくので—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:08.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,より協力的になってくれます\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:12.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,そして 自分もできると\N理解してくれます\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:16.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,さらに 各医療機関情報デスクには—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:19.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,協力的な医師のリストが\N保管されています\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:23.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,彼らは権威ある医師たちで—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:28.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,とても複雑で困難な症例でも\N無輸血で治療を行なうことを—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:33.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,他の医師と協議したり\N説得したりすることに慣れています\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:39.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,ある日 わたしが深夜に\N電話を受けると—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:45.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,出産の時に大量出血した\N姉妹に関する情報が飛び込んできました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:50.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,担当した医師は\N切実に助けを必要としていました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:54.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,わたしたちは\Nカナダで非常に権威ある—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:58.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,協力的な産婦人科の教授に\N電話しました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:02.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,わたしは第一声—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:07.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,“真夜中に電話して大変\N 申し訳ございません”と言いました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:09.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,すると教授は—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,“謝らないでください マーク”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:15.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,“いつでも姉妹たちを助けられて\N 嬉しいです”と言われました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,もちろん 教授は証人ではありません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:22.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,しかし自分の姉妹のように\N見てくださり—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:25.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,助けたいと願ってくださいました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:29.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,このような\N勇敢で熟練した医師たちが—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:33.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,世界中で大勢の兄弟たちを助けています\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:37.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,ツールも改良し続けています\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,皆さんもjw.orgにある—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:47.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,「臨床医のための医学情報」サイトを\N ご存じでしょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:49.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,繰り返しになりますが—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:53.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,このサイトはエホバの証人向けでは\Nありません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:56.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,医療の専門家向けのサイトです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:08:03.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,最近作られたものですが\N既に素晴らしい成果を挙げています\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,経験をご紹介しましょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:09.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,ある姉妹が書かれたものです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:13.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,“最近 夫と救急病院に行き—”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:16.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,“わたしの盲腸の近くに\N 大きな腫瘍が見つかって—”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:21.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,“とても難しい手術が必要だと\N 言われました”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:26.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,“担当した外科医は\N わたしがエホバの証人であり—”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:31.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,“妥協しようとしないので\N 動揺されました”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:36.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,“医師は取り乱しませんでしたが\N とても困惑していました”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:40.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,“夫は兄弟と電話をしに\N 席を外しました”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:43.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,“5分後に研修医が来て—”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:50.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,“さっきの外科医がjw.orgで\N 情報を見に行ったと伝えました”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:52.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,“ウェブサイトについては\N 話していませんでした”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:55.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,“どこでどうやって知ったかは\N 分かりません”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:09:00.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,“10分後 外科医が情報を印刷して\N 戻ってきました”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:02.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,“それを読んでしるしをつけ—”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:06.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,“わたしたちと共に\N 内容ひとつひとつを網羅しました”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:09.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,“そしてわたしの手を取って\N 微笑みました”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,“準備はいいかと尋ね—”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:15.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,“わたしのためにベストを尽くすと\N 約束されました”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:21.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,“彼も生涯妥協しないことを\N 神に誓っていたそうです”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:28.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,“手術の半日後 わたしはその医師に\N 問題がなかったかと聞きました”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:32.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,“「いいえ \N 大変素晴らしいものでした」”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:35.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,“その答えから\N 医療機関連絡委員会や—”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:40.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,“エホバが備えてくださった情報が\N医師の役に立ったんだと分かりました”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:43.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,姉妹は結論でこう述べています\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:46.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,“真理のうちに歩む人生の中で—”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:50.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,“エホバからの平和を\N これほど感じたことはありません”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:56.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバは奇跡的に病気を回復するとは\N約束しておられませんが—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:10:01.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,支えと力を与えると保証しておられます\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:06.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,医療機関連絡委員会の良い働きは—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:10.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバからの素晴らしい贈りものです！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:14.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,それでわたしたちはこれからも\N次の指示に従ってまいりましょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:14.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,“血[を]避けなさい”\N
